parameters.description: Log intrinsic coral growth rate (year^-1). The actual growth rate is exp(log_growth_rate).
Log feeding (predation) rate of COTS on corals (per year per coral unit). The actual rate is exp(log_feeding_rate).
Log baseline Crown-of-Thorns starfish abundance (individuals/m2). The actual abundance is exp(log_cots_base).
Log impact rate on slow-growing corals. The actual impact rate is exp(log_impact_rate_slow).
Log impact rate on fast-growing corals. The actual impact rate is exp(log_impact_rate_fast).
